Proto:  Clean Up the Map

Rule 1706 is amended by replacing all instances of "the Origin" with
"Town Square".

     The following Locations are destroyed:

     * Government Building #2
     * Government Building #3
     * Government Building #4
     * Justiciar's Chambers
     * Rulekeepor's Office
     * Agoran Colors Society
     * Notary's Office

     The following Locations are renamed:

     * Government Building #1 -> City Hall
     * Promotor's Office -> Soap Box

     The following pairs of Locations become Adjacent:

     * Town Square, Welcoming Center
     * Town Square, Stasis Chamber
     * City Hall, Green Dome
     * City Hall, Registration Desk
     * Welcoming Center, Registration Desk
     * City Hall, Soap Box
     * City Hall, Voting Booth
     * Soap Box, Voting Booth
     * City Hall, Courthouse
     * City Hall, Mad Scientist's Lab
     * City Hall, Wizard's Castle
     * Town Square, University
     * Town Square, Beer Hall
     * University, Beer Hall

Create a Rule entitled "Vote in the Voting Booth" with this text:

     At the end of each Nomic Week, the Cartographor shall pay out 1 VT to
     each Player who cast at least one Vote on a Proposal during that week,
     and cast all eir Votes on Proposals that week while eir Location was
     the Voting Booth.

Create a Rule entitled "Propose from the Soap Box" with this text:

     At the end of each Nomic Week, the Cartographor shall pay out 1 P-Note
     to each Player who made at least one Proposal during that week, and
     made all eir Proposals that week while eir Location was the Soap Box.

